# This directory holds metaltile-generated artifacts:
#   kernels.metallib   — pre-compiled Metal binary (gitignored)
#   manifest.json      — per-kernel metadata (gitignored)
#   kernels/*.metal    — MSL sources for inspection (gitignored)
#
# Files are produced by `cargo run -p metaltile-emit` (sibling metaltile
# repo) and consumed by the SPM build plugin. See planning/plan.md
# Phase 0.
